  <!-- EN: manalope -->
  <GR_Manalope.label>爆炸人</GR_Manalope.label>
  <!-- EN: A floating, ticking time bomb that produces extremely reactive chemicals instead of chemfuel. Arguably more of a complex chemical distillery than an animal, it's a scientific miracle that it doesn’t explode every time it coughs. Surprisingly effective in combat in ways the enemy would really have preferred not knowing.\n\nA humanoid hybrid with recessive boomalope genes. Thanks to its sac filled with buoyant chemicals, this hybrid never touches the ground and simply floats from location to location. Ignores terrain penalty costs and traps, while also being able to set down explosive traps of its own.\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Gameplay effect:</color> Humanoid hybrids will periodically engage other colonists in conversation, talking about a variety of topics. This increases the social recreation needs of those they interact with by 10% (subject to diminishing returns like all joy types). If using Ideology, humanoid hybrids are subject to precepts. Set trap ability: once every 3 days the manalope can set up an explosive IED. Hovers over terrain, ignoring terrain costs, and doesn't trigger ANY traps. -->
  <GR_Manalope.description>爆炸人能够依靠爆炸囊内特殊的氢气-化合燃料混合物质漂浮在半空中。他们的身体构造更像是一种复杂的化学精炼器，而且奇迹般的不会在咳嗽时就直接爆炸。他们还可以将身上的爆炸囊取下来做成陷阱，但敌人肯定不会想知道自己是被什么炸死的。\n\n【性状基因I】：人类基因\n【性状基因II】：爆炸基因\n【基本特征】：野性较高，可训练度中等，不会受到地形带来的移动速度惩罚。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C>游戏效果：&lt;/color>人类混种生物偶尔会与其他殖民者聊天，并增加大约10%的娱乐值。如果安装了文化DLC，人类混种生物也会受到新增戒律的影响。\n\n所有爆炸混种生物死后都会产生爆炸，部分还会带有一些特殊效果。\n\n爆炸人死亡后会产生小范围的酸蚀爆炸，它们拥有特殊能力“安置爆炸陷阱”。</GR_Manalope.description>
  <!-- EN: head -->
  <GR_Manalope.tools.head.label>头</GR_Manalope.tools.head.label>
  
  <!-- EN: manbear -->
  <GR_Manbear.label>熊人</GR_Manbear.label>
  <!-- EN: What it lacks in ferocity, it makes up for in tenacity and formidable cuteness. What person, sane or insane, could reject the diplomatic arguments presented by a waist-high teddy bear with a face just begging to be pinched. Not that you actually would, as those sharp teeth remind one that it very likely prefers to debate with its food before eating it.\n\nA humanoid hybrid with recessive ursine genes. Absolutely terrible in combat potential despite its genetic material, but it is surprisingly adept at convincing prisoners to join the colony.\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Gameplay effect:</color> Humanoid hybrids will periodically engage other colonists in conversation, talking about a variety of topics. This increases the social recreation needs of those they interact with by 10% (subject to diminishing returns like all joy types). If using Ideology, humanoid hybrids are subject to precepts. Menbear are adept conversationalists and will help in recruiting prisoners. -->
  <GR_Manbear.description>或许你曾以为熊人肯定会是些凶猛无比的生物，但它们却出人意料地像可爱的泰迪熊。虽然有着十分锋利的牙齿，但比起撕咬与杀戮，它们可能更喜欢在吃饭前先和食物争论一番。无论是思维清晰的正常人还是胡言乱语的疯子，在那捏起来软乎乎的脸蛋面前，没人能拒绝它们提出的“小小请求”。\n\n【性状基因I】：人类基因\n【性状基因II】：熊类基因\n【基本特征】：野性高，可训练度中等。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C>游戏效果：&lt;/color>人类混种生物偶尔会与其他殖民者聊天，并增加大约10%的娱乐值。如果安装了文化DLC，人类混种生物也会受到新增戒律的影响。熊人可以协助招募囚犯。</GR_Manbear.description>
  <!-- EN: left fist -->
  <GR_Manbear.tools.left_fist.label>左拳</GR_Manbear.tools.left_fist.label>
  <!-- EN: right fist -->
  <GR_Manbear.tools.right_fist.label>右拳</GR_Manbear.tools.right_fist.label>
  <!-- EN: head -->
  <GR_Manbear.tools.head.label>头</GR_Manbear.tools.head.label>
  
  <!-- EN: mancat -->
  <GR_Mancat.label>猫人</GR_Mancat.label>
  <!-- EN: A creature originally designed for other recreational purposes before that particular laboratory of degenerates got glassed from orbit, they make for an affectionate conversation partner. You know, probably, most likely, until their particular speech pattern grinds on your nerves like a cheese grater.\n\nA humanoid hybrid with recessive feline genes. A surprisingly large yet timid predator that can output a disturbing amount of damage. Typically fun to talk to, but 10% of the time it tries to be a little too cute.\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Gameplay effect:</color> Like all cat hybrids, they have an improved melee dodge ability and a short nuzzle period. Humanoid hybrids will periodically engage other colonists in conversation, talking about a variety of topics. This increases the social recreation needs of those they interact with (subject to diminishing returns like all joy types). In the case of the mancat, these interactions will 90% of the time increase the targets' social joy by 15%, but the rest of the time they'll just make the target very annoyed... If using Ideology, humanoid hybrids are subject to precepts. -->
  <GR_Mancat.description>猫人最初是作为一种娱乐消遣品而被创造出来的...是的，曾经是这样。虽然他们在大部分时候都是很棒的聊天对象，但他们特殊的语言模式偶尔会像奶酪擦丝器一样折磨你的精神。\n\n【性状基因I】：人类基因\n【性状基因II】：猫科基因\n【基本特征】：野性高，可训练度高。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C>游戏效果：&lt;/color>人类混种生物偶尔会与其他殖民者聊天，并增加大约10%的娱乐值。如果安装了文化DLC，人类混种生物也会受到新增戒律的影响。猫人在与其他殖民者聊天时会增加大约15%的娱乐值，但也会有小概率把他们惹毛。</GR_Mancat.description>
  <!-- EN: head -->
  <GR_Mancat.tools.head.label>头</GR_Mancat.tools.head.label>
  
  <!-- EN: manchicken -->
  <GR_Manchicken.label>鸡人</GR_Manchicken.label>
  <!-- EN: “You know how, like, chicken tastes, like, so good? So what if, like, we made a chicken that, y’know, when you killed it you could, I dunno, stuff it right in your mouth as fried chicken? Dude, this shit is the shit, where did you get this, man?” - Recording playback used in a hearing against a disgraced genetic scientist for misappropriating government funding.\n\nA humanoid hybrid with recessive avian genes. A very valuable hybrid that convinces people that its greatest desire in life is to be eaten. When butchered, it leaves large amounts of completely healthy and nutritious meat that can be eaten as-is.\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Gameplay effect:</color> Humanoid hybrids will periodically engage other colonists in conversation, talking about a variety of topics. This increases the social recreation needs of those they interact with by 10% (subject to diminishing returns like all joy types). If using Ideology, humanoid hybrids are subject to precepts. Doesn't lay eggs, but can be butchered for large amounts of a very nutritive meat that doesn't have poisoning chance and takes 6 days to rot. -->
  <GR_Manchicken.description>“你知道，为什么鸡肉这么香吗？那么假如，假如我们创造出了一种鸡，呃，当我们把它宰了后，咳，我不知道该怎么形容，可以直接把它的肉像炸鸡一样塞到嘴里？啧，兄啊，你们到底是怎么他妈搞出这些狗屎玩意的？”——这段录音来自于某场为指控基因科学家私吞政府公款而举行的听证会。\n\n【性状基因I】：人类基因\n【性状基因II】：禽类基因\n【基本特征】：野性较高，需要关在畜栏里。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C>游戏效果：&lt;/color>人类混种生物偶尔会与其他殖民者聊天，并增加大约10%的娱乐值。如果安装了文化DLC，人类混种生物也会受到新增戒律的影响。鸡人无法产蛋，他们最大的作用就是屠宰产肉。这些肉营养值很高，即使生吃也不会引起食物中毒，腐烂速度也更慢一些。</GR_Manchicken.description>
