  <GR_Manchicken.tools.claws.label>爪</GR_Manchicken.tools.claws.label>
  <!-- EN: head -->
  <GR_Manchicken.tools.head.label>头</GR_Manchicken.tools.head.label>
  
  <!-- EN: manffalo -->
  <GR_Manffalo.label>雪牛人</GR_Manffalo.label>
  <!-- EN: Considered a straight upgrade from their progenitor, featured several times in Cannibal Monthly. Produces appreciable amounts of wool and milk, it is a living, breathing reference to the phrase “what does not kill me makes me stronger”. At least, when it comes to hauling large loads, which is all some people care about.\n\nA humanoid hybrid with recessive muffalo genes. Capable of surviving very high temperatures in opposition to the traditional use of muffalos, this hybrid performs below average for a pack animal. However, due to adaptive muscle and skeletal structure, the more it participates as part of a caravan, the heavier the load it can withstand.\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Gameplay effect:</color> Humanoid hybrids will periodically engage other colonists in conversation, talking about a variety of topics. This increases the social recreation needs of those they interact with by 10% (subject to diminishing returns like all joy types). If using Ideology, humanoid hybrids are subject to precepts. The manffalo starts as a poor caravaning animal, but learns as time progresses. Every hour spent in a caravan will increase its cargo capacity by 1%, up to a maximum of a 100% increase from base. -->
  <GR_Manffalo.description>雪牛人正是“杀不死你的东西，只会让你变得更加强大”这句名言的最好佐证。虽然驮运能力天生较低，但他们具有自适应性的肌肉与骨骼可以通过不断运动和学习来逐渐提高自身的载重。\n\n【性状基因I】：人类基因\n【性状基因II】：雪牛基因\n【基本特征】：野性高，能驮运，能产奶和毛，需要关在畜栏里。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C>游戏效果：&lt;/color>人类混种生物偶尔会与其他殖民者聊天，并增加大约10%的娱乐值。如果安装了文化DLC，人类混种生物也会受到新增戒律的影响。当处于远行队中时，雪牛人的载重每小时会提高1%。最多能够提高100%的载重。</GR_Manffalo.description>
  <!-- EN: head -->
  <GR_Manffalo.tools.head.label>头</GR_Manffalo.tools.head.label>
  
  <!-- EN: mansquirrel -->
  <GR_Mansquirrel.label>松鼠人</GR_Mansquirrel.label>
  <!-- EN: A bloody weird little thing that hates the cold with a passion, and will take any opportunity to clear away snow from its home. Given that they are active at nighttime, they make a great conversational companion for those otherwise asocial Night Owls you keep gathering.\n\nA humanoid hybrid with recessive rodent genes. Quite quick for their size and unusually a nocturnal animal, they make for a fast, social and quick-breeding hybrid. Will shovel snow if there are Clear Snow zones set up.\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Gameplay effect:</color> Humanoid hybrids will periodically engage other colonists in conversation, talking about a variety of topics. This increases the social recreation needs of those they interact with by 10% (subject to diminishing returns like all joy types). If using Ideology, humanoid hybrids are subject to precepts. The mansquirrel is a nocturnal animal that sleeps during the day. Will obey orders to clear snow around the colony. -->
  <GR_Mansquirrel.description>这些古里古怪的小家伙非常讨厌寒冷。只要还能正常活动，他们就会积极地清扫殖民地附近的积雪。鉴于松鼠人昼伏夜出的习性，拥有“夜猫子”特性的殖民者或许会和他们合得来。\n\n【性状基因I】：人类基因\n【性状基因II】：啮齿类/兔类基因\n【基本特征】：野性高，可训练度中等，移动速度快，繁殖速度快。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C>游戏效果：&lt;/color>人类混种生物偶尔会与其他殖民者聊天，并增加大约10%的娱乐值。如果安装了文化DLC，人类混种生物也会受到新增戒律的影响。松鼠人是一种夜行性生物，他们会主动清扫除雪区内的积雪。</GR_Mansquirrel.description>
  <!-- EN: left claw -->
  <GR_Mansquirrel.tools.left_claw.label>左爪</GR_Mansquirrel.tools.left_claw.label>
  <!-- EN: right claw -->
  <GR_Mansquirrel.tools.right_claw.label>右爪</GR_Mansquirrel.tools.right_claw.label>
  <!-- EN: head -->
  <GR_Mansquirrel.tools.head.label>头</GR_Mansquirrel.tools.head.label>
  
  <!-- EN: manwolf -->
  <GR_Manwolf.label>狼人</GR_Manwolf.label>
  <!-- EN: Possibly either the ancestor to the warg or an attempt at creating a successor, the team in charge of making this particular hybrid clearly had read one to many mythological novels. Arguably there’s no transformation at the full moon, so you just get the permanent single form, but there’s no pleasing some people.\n\nA humanoid hybrid with recessive canine genes. A fast and dangerous hunter with almost misplaced self-confidence. Also very intelligent and possessing faint regenerative capabilities. Extremely hardy but also extremely restrictive in their diet.\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Gameplay effect:</color> Humanoid hybrids will periodically engage other colonists in conversation, talking about a variety of topics. This increases the social recreation needs of those they interact with by 10% (subject to diminishing returns like all joy types). If using Ideology, humanoid hybrids are subject to precepts. -->
  <GR_Manwolf.description>这些人类混种生物很可能是座狼的原型，他们的创造者显然读过不少神话小说。人狼在战斗中的表现异常可靠，唯一的缺憾可能就是无法在满月下变身了。\n\n【性状基因I】：人类基因\n【性状基因II】：犬科基因\n【基本特征】：野性高，可训练度高，移动速度快。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C>游戏效果：&lt;/color>人类混种生物偶尔会与其他殖民者聊天，并增加大约10%的娱乐值。如果安装了文化DLC，人类混种生物也会受到新增戒律的影响。\n\n大部分犬科混种生物都拥有特殊能力“肾上腺素激发”，使用后其移动速度将会在短时间内翻倍，过后则会陷入长达半天的力竭状态。\n\n人狼拥有一定的自愈再生能力。</GR_Manwolf.description>
